ntribution from more distant clusters becomes\nprogressively more diluted by the WMAP beam. We can, however, at present not\nrule out that these more distant clusters simply contribute less to the overall\nmotion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Oct 2009 19:06:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Oct 2009 15:54:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 11 Mar 2010 02:57:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
